description: Try our easy to follow Rhubarb, Strawberry & Apple Strudel recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Rhubarb, Strawberry & Apple Strudel Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake for 30 minutes or until pastry is crisp and golden. Cool strudel on tray for 5 minutes. Dust with icing sugar, slice and serve with reserved syrup and extra strawberries.
